.TH "ImThreshold User Manual" 1 "19 Dec 2017" "ImThreshold documentation"

.SH NAME
imthreshold-fbgfglsep

.SH DESCRIPTION
DjVuL thresholds an image (Multi-scale binarization).

.SH SYNOPSIS
imthreshold-fbgfglsep [options] <input_file> <input_mask_file>(BW) <output_fg_file> <output_bg_file>

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
-c N
clean blur radius (int, optional, default = 0)
.TP
-b N
base block size (int, optional, default = 3)
.TP
-f N
foreground divide (int, optional, default = 2)
.TP
-l N
level (int, optional, default = 10)
.TP
-o N.N
overlay (double, optional, default = 0.5)
.TP
-h
help

.SH EXAMPLE
imthreshold-tdjvu sample.tif bw.djvul.tif fg.djvul.tif bg.djvul.tif

